    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but even the \"next minute\" is just more pain. it's just more cold and more blood. i look at the horizon and i don't see anything coming. it just feels like we're prolonging the inevitable. wouldn't it be more peaceful if we just... stopped trying to fight the dark?",
